cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) categories since it deals with dense video captioning, which requires both visual and linguistic understanding. The use of reinforcement learning also suggests that it may belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. Additionally, the paper involves modeling temporal dependency and contextual reasoning, which are common themes in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) research. Finally, since the proposed technique achieves outstanding performances on ActivityNet Captions dataset, it may also belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category.
